    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing and performing exactly as it did the day it was first delivered. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like finish without a single swirl mark, chip, or scratch. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state, with the upholstery and surfaces showing zero signs of use or wear. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously stored and maintained to preserve its original integrity. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine example that will satisfy even the most discerning collector.",
      "price": 49500.0,
